Roaming around Colombo felt like walking on the streets of Mumbai — the vintage charm, the architecture, the chaos… all so familiar, yet so fresh! 🌴🏙️

Took my hungry soul to Ministry of Crab — a legendary seafood spot tucked inside the Old Dutch Hospital precinct (yes, a hospital turned heritage hangout!). 🏛️🦀 The place isn’t just about food — it’s a whole vibe. The profits go into promoting local produce and seafood sustainability, which made my heart (and stomach) very happy!

Oh, and forget forks — they literally encourage you to eat with your hands, so you can go ahead and get messy — it’s all part of the experience. 💅🫳

#ColomboFeels #MumbaiMeetsColombo #MinistryOfCrab #SeafoodGoals #TravelWithTaste #manaliinsrilanka
